      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;-about-me&#34;&gt;👋 About Me&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I was born in 2002 in the beautiful northern Chinese province of 黑龙江 (heilongjiang), and immigrated to Canada with my family when I was just 2 years old. Nowadays, I’m an average software developer with a healthy dose of imposter syndrome.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m currently employed as a &lt;strong&gt;Software Developer&lt;/strong&gt; at &lt;strong&gt;J.D. Power&lt;/strong&gt;, where I have worked since 2023.  I develop critical data processing pipelines and backend services in both batch and stream processing flows.  I have a strong background in Java, and Go.  I am active in LGBTQ+ advocacy at my company, giving feedback on inclusive language, and joining the pride panel in 2024.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
